# Render Deployment Configuration

This project is deployed on Render with the following configuration.

## üöÄ Production URLs

- **Frontend**: https://simon-game-frontend-nqu6.onrender.com
- **Backend**: https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com

## üì¶ Services

### Backend: simon-game-backend

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Service ID** | srv-d5hprhmmcj7s73b6bhtg |
| **Type** | Web Service |
| **Runtime** | Node.js |
| **Plan** | Starter ($7/month) |
| **Region** | Oregon |
| **URL** | https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com |
| **Dashboard** | https://dashboard.render.com/web/srv-d5hprhmmcj7s73b6bhtg |
| **Branch** | main |
| **Auto Deploy** | Yes (on commit) |

**Build Configuration:**
- Build Command: `npm install && npm run build`
- Start Command: `npm start`
- Port: 10000

**Environment Variables:**
```
NODE_ENV=production
PORT=10000
FRONTEND_URL=https://simon-game-frontend-nqu6.onrender.com
JWT_SECRET=<generated-secret>
```

### Frontend: simon-game-frontend

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
