| **Type** | Static Site |
| **Plan** | Free |
| **URL** | https://simon-game-frontend-nqu6.onrender.com |
| **Dashboard** | https://dashboard.render.com/static/srv-d5hpojh4tr6s739p37j0 |
| **Branch** | main |
| **Auto Deploy** | Yes (on commit) |

**Build Configuration:**
- Build Command: `cd frontend && npm install && npm run build`
- Publish Path: `frontend/dist`

**Environment Variables:**
```
VITE_API_URL=https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com
VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com
```

