### Automatic Deployment
Push to the `main` branch to trigger automatic deployment of both services.

## üìã Environment Variable Reference

### Backend Required Variables
| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `NODE_ENV` | Environment mode | `production` |
| `PORT` | Server port | `10000` |
| `FRONTEND_URL` | Frontend URL for CORS | `https://simon-game-frontend-nqu6.onrender.com` |
| `JWT_SECRET` | Secret for JWT tokens | Auto-generated |

### Frontend Required Variables
| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `VITE_API_URL` | Backend API URL | `https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com` |
| `VITE_SOCKET_URL` | WebSocket server URL | `https://simon-game-backend-ljcp.onrender.com` |

## üîí Security Notes

- JWT_SECRET should never be committed to the repository
- All environment variables are configured in Render dashboard
- HTTPS is enforced on all Render URLs

